<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>お知らせ</title>
    <style>
header {
  width: 100%;
  background-color: #000000;
  padding: 10px 0;
  text-align: left;
}

.banner {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: flex-start;
  padding-left: 15px;
}

.banner .btn {
  color: #ffffff;
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-right: 20px;
}

.main {
  flex: 1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
  width: 100%;
}

.search-bar {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 50px;
}

.search-bar .form-control {
   padding: 10px;
   width: 300px;
   border: 1px solid #cccccc;
   border-radius: 4px;
}

.search-bar .btn-search {
   padding: 10px;
   background-color: #333333;
   color: white;
   border: none;
   border-radius: 4px;
   margin-left: 10px;
}
        .announcement {
            border: 2px solid #ddd;
            border-radius: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #fff;
            display: flex;
        }

        .announcement-icon {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            background-image: url('https://cdn.glitch.global/441c91ae-2a7f-4142-9ffb-ab0c7066dfa1/IMG_1281.png?v=1718682861752');
            background-size: cover;
            margin-right: 15px;
            cursor: pointer;
        }

        .announcement-details {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .announcement h2 {
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            color: #333;
        }

        .announcement .timestamp {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #888;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .announcement p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #555;
        }

        .profile-card {
            display: none;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #ccc;
            padding: 10px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        .announcement-icon:hover + .announcement-details .profile-card {
            display: block;
        }
      .usuimoji {
         font-size: 12px;
         color: #888;
         margin-bottom: 10px;
         font-weight: 300; 
      }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <header>
    <div class="banner">
      <button class="btn btn-link" onclick="window.location.href='/'">ホーム🏠</button>
      <button class="btn btn-link" onclick="window.location.href='/blog'">お知らせ</button>
      <!-- 他のボタンもここに追加できます -->
      <form class="d-flex" action="/s">
        <input type="text" name="q" class="form-control" placeholder="キーワードを入力..." required>
      </form>
      <button class="btn btn-link" style="position: absolute; right: 10px;" onclick="window.location.href='/send'">問い合わせ</button>
    </div>
  </header>
  <p class="usuimoji">※この見た目は仕様です、ブログっぽいでしょ？(偏見</p>
    <div class="announcement">
        <div class="announcement-icon"></div>
        <div class="announcement-details">
            <h2>再生成功！</h2>
            <p class="timestamp">投稿時間: 2024年6月18日 14:41</p>
            <p>再生＆ダウンロードが動くことを確認！よっしゃあああああああ。再生はできるけどダウンロード出来るサイトがなくて困ってたんよな＼(^ω^)／</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="announcement">
        <div class="announcement-icon"></div>
        <div class="announcement-details">
            <h2>サイト作成</h2>
            <p class="timestamp">投稿時間: 2024年6月17日 13:15</p>
            <p>簡単に再生＆ダウンロード出来るサイトを作成中です...</p>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-card">
            <h3>わかめ02</h3>
            <p>あたままっしろ</p>
        </div>
    </div>


</body>

</html>
